{"tid":914543,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"環保撚幫東江水賣廣告","createTime":"2018-11-24T11:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T00:25:38.000Z","uid":192517,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"663bc8425dbe73679f09fe6b60ebe5a6f776a3ec","tid":914543,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/914514/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/914514/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n見唔到都算 一見就想飲 即刻飲左幾啖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識飲一定就咁飲水喉水既原味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n發起一人一東江水運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等陣番屋企即刻飲<br />\n<br />\n收工即去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來覺得好難飲，一陣再番屋企試下<br />\n<br />\n即刻儲番幾十支 企係綠色和平門口慢慢飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫佢叫外賣<br />\n東江水配 pizza <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOk 今晚飲個番尋味<br />\n<br />\n以行動支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115b15cee3a54ac6d7279b27ba6580637d4c7dfd","tid":914543,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:02:32.000Z","msg":"好想飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到個post唔飲都想儲幾支入雪櫃"},{"pid":"916ba51480489091a746b305fe808e611919290e","tid":914543,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - irregular<br />\n正on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日又多樣見識"},{"pid":"293ce12a9449ae73b81c7a8ef03aac4e73dbb4bb","tid":914543,"uid":192517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"最鍾意飲東江水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfeebf27bf1d86c26095bee14d1f3bf2095005f","tid":914543,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T13:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=lo6itg/5o4p000353nr23os958r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dlo6itg%2F5o4p000353nr23os958r.jpg&h=7465144b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係咪要比環保撚捉去勞改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：東江水愛好者"},{"pid":"f016868158108cb38dc236c39c4b5cbc49b52cac","tid":914543,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T17:01:59.000Z","msg":"驚以後無得飲<br />\n即刻儲番十箱先"},{"pid":"15c6d588c2173523437285079a2b66c37760695b","tid":914543,"uid":64601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T19:34:47.000Z","msg":"說好的要同環保撚唱反調呢"},{"pid":"53c846b5e77b1e16929ac092b3f6db374c8a46f7","tid":914543,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T22:18:45.000Z","msg":"嚇到我即刻儲十幾支東江水係綠色和平門口派街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260b5649956dccc9f4f9e51e61e4106debdcbdcd","tid":914543,"uid":192517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"我見到東江水想飲就非黑即白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你見到唔係環保撚就係反環保撚<br />\n<br />\n邊個先係非黑即白屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgm